  <brief_title>Single Versus Multiple Visits Endodontic Treatment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Healing Rates After Single Versus Multiple Visits Endodontic Treatment of Necrotic Teeth With Apical Periodontitis: A Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
